$8ˆc<?php exit; ?>a:1:{s:7:"content";O:8:"stdClass":24:{s:2:"ID";i:13;s:11:"post_author";s:1:"3";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2022-06-03 05:03:05";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2022-06-03 05:03:05";s:12:"post_content";s:12724:"[et_pb_section fb_built="1" fullwidth="on" _builder_version="4.17.4" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_fullwidth_header title=" Allergy Management: Get assistance immediately!" subhead="Call 97462 22668 now" button_one_text="Call Directly from Mobile" button_one_url="tel:9746222668" _builder_version="4.17.6" _module_preset="default" title_font="Francois One|700|||||||" title_text_color="#FFFFFF" title_font_size="40px" subhead_font="Francois One|700|||||||" subhead_font_size="30px" subhead_line_height="1.8em" background_enable_color="off" use_background_color_gradient="on" background_color_gradient_stops="rgba(0,0,0,0.13) 0%|rgba(0,0,0,0.62) 100%" background_color_gradient_overlays_image="on" background_image="https://www.allergytest.in/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/BANNER-1.jpeg" custom_button_one="on" button_one_text_color="#FFFFFF" button_one_bg_color="#ff4100" button_one_border_width="0px" button_one_font="Dosis|500|||||||" custom_padding="152px||152px||true|" title_font_size_tablet="40px" title_font_size_phone="30px" title_font_size_last_edited="on|phone" subhead_font_size_tablet="30px" subhead_font_size_phone="25px" subhead_font_size_last_edited="on|phone" global_colors_info="{}"][/et_pb_fullwidth_header][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" _builder_version="4.17.4" _module_preset="default" custom_padding="25px|||||" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.17.4" _module_preset="default" custom_padding="||0px|||" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.17.4" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.17.4" _module_preset="default" header_font="Francois One|700|||||||" header_text_color="#000000" header_font_size="35px" header_line_height="1.3em" custom_margin="||8px|||" header_font_size_tablet="35px" header_font_size_phone="25px" header_font_size_last_edited="on|phone" global_colors_info="{}"]<h1 class="mbr-fonts-style mbr-title align-left pb-3 display-2" style="text-align: center;">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
<h1 style="text-align: center;"></h1>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.17.4" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.17.4" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_accordion open_toggle_text_color="#000000" icon_color="#af0c00" use_icon_font_size="on" icon_font_size="19px" _builder_version="4.17.5" _module_preset="default" toggle_text_color="#000000" toggle_font="Francois One||||||||" toggle_font_size="16px" body_font="Dosis||||||||" body_text_align="justify" body_text_color="#000000" body_font_size="16px" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_accordion_item title=" What kind of test is this?" open="on" _builder_version="4.17.5" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}"]<p><span>This is a blood test that will reveal the exact cause of your allergy.</span></p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title="How much time it takes?" _builder_version="4.17.5" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}" open="off"]<p><span>It takes just 10-15 minutes to collect the blood sample.</span></p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title="How long it takes to get the result?" _builder_version="4.17.5" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}" open="off"]<p><span>It takes 5 days to receive the test results.</span></p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title="How to I get the report?" _builder_version="4.17.5" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}" open="off"]<p><span>The report is sent by WhatsApp, E-mail as well as the hard copy by post.</span></p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title="Is fasting required?" _builder_version="4.17.5" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}" open="off"]<p><span>No fasting is required for this test.</span></p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title="I am on allergy medication. Can I take the test?" _builder_version="4.17.5" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}" open="off"]<p><span>There should be 24 hrs gap between the last medication and blood sample </span><span>collection. If you are on steroids a minimum 7 days gap should be there.</span></p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title="Which is the best test for allergy? Skin testing or blood testing?" _builder_version="4.17.5" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}" open="off"]<p><span>Skin tests are good if you want to test for a few items. The blood test is ideal for </span><span>large panels and it is not painful as well as quick.</span></p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title="What causes an allergic reaction?" _builder_version="4.17.5" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}" open="off"]<p><span>Allergy reaction happens when the body resists a particular intake. </span><span>The test is done to identify those items.</span></p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title="How accurate is blood test." _builder_version="4.17.4" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}" open="off"]<p><span>Its accuracy is 85-95%</span></p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title="Do I need a doctorâ€™s prescription to take the test?" _builder_version="4.17.5" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}" open="off"]<p><span>Doctor prescription not required to take the test</span></p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title="Should I take a Comprehensive test or I can take a smaller panel?" _builder_version="4.17.5" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}" open="off"]<p><span>For those with serious allergy problems, we recommend a comprehensive test.</span></p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title="Do you have a Doctor for consulting?" _builder_version="4.17.5" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}" open="off"]<p><span>We have Allergy Specialist for consulting over telephone.</span></p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title="After testing what medication I should take " _builder_version="4.17.5" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}" open="off"]<p><span>After testing you wonâ€™t need any medication. Simply avoiding the items </span><span>specified in the report will free you from allergy problems.</span></p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title="Why the test is expensive?" _builder_version="4.17.5" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}" open="off"]<p><span>It is not a single blood test, we need to test over 180+ items to identify the </span><span>causes of your allergy.</span></p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=" Are the prices fixed " _builder_version="4.17.5" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}" open="off"]<p><span>Yes. The prices are uniform all over the country.</span></p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title="Can I pay with a credit/debit card?" _builder_version="4.17.5" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}" open="off"]<p><span>Yes, we accept Credit/Debit card, Net banking, Google Pay, PayTM and cash.</span></p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title="Which cities are you operating?" _builder_version="4.17.5" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}" open="off"]<p style="text-align: justify;"><span>We directly operate from Bengaluru, Chennai, Hyderabad, Kochi and Trivandrum. Other locations we operate through associated labs when requirement arises.</span></p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title="Is Allergy and Intolerance are the same?" _builder_version="4.17.5" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}" open="off"]<p style="text-align: justify;"><span>No. While allergy is the bodyâ€™s response to things that it doesnâ€™t accept, intolerance is the bodyâ€™s inability to digest an item properly. </span><span>Allergic reactions can occur almost immediately whereas an intolerance reaction can sometimes present itself up to 72 hours later.Â </span></p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title="Can you do a particular item outside your panels?" _builder_version="4.17.5" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}" open="off"]<p style="text-align: justify;"><span>No. We can do tests with the panels we have only.</span></p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][/et_pb_accordion][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" module_id="2" module_class="2" _builder_version="4.17.6" _module_preset="default" use_background_color_gradient="on" background_color_gradient_stops="rgba(255,255,255,0.7) 0%|rgba(255,255,255,0.59) 99%" background_color_gradient_overlays_image="on" background_image="https://www.allergytest.in/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/row-bgimg-1.jpeg" parallax="on" parallax_method="off" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.17.4" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.17.4" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.18.0" _module_preset="default" header_font="Francois One|700|||||||" header_text_color="#000000" header_font_size="35px" header_letter_spacing="1px" header_line_height="1.3em" custom_margin="||8px|||" custom_padding="||||false|false" header_font_size_tablet="35px" header_font_size_phone="25px" header_font_size_last_edited="on|phone" global_colors_info="{}"]<h1 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Mumbai, Chennai, Bengaluru, Hyderabad, Trivandrum, Kochi &amp; Pune.</strong></h1>
